data.title: Harlequins in San Francisco for Reception & SFGG Summer Camp
data.meta_description: Harlequins, USA Club Rugby, USA Youth Rugby
data.text:
Harlequins Release

Premiership Club Harlequins Rugby Union are organizing a Drinks Reception at the City Club of San Francisco on Wednesday June 15 6:00-8:30PM.

Meet and hear from Tony Diprose (Harlequins Academy & Global Development Director), and Will Skinner (Harlequins Head of Business Development and former captain). Address inquiries to atlanta.stjohn@quins.co.uk or RSVP here:

https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/an-introduction-to-harlequins-in-the-usa-drinks-reception-tickets-25969516523

The Harlequins will also be at the SFGG Youth & HS Summer Camp on Tuesday June 14 1-3PM running a special High School Academy session at SFGG on Treasure Island. For more information and sign up: https://2016sfggsummercamp.eventbrite.com

https://djcoilrugby.com/
